    "title": "京东开放平台发布违规宣传信息细则",
    "followRuleId": "922769750780678144",
    "content": "<h1 id=\"heading-0\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 13pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 16pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; break-after: avoid; font-family: '等线 Light';\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">夸大或虚构功能功效：指商家在商品宣传中声称该商品具备某种特殊功效或特性，但实际商品并未包含相关功能、功效、资质或证明。或商家在商品描述、广告、营销活动或其他渠道中对商品的性能、效果或特点进行不实或过度夸张的宣传，导致消费者形成错误的预期，认为商品能够实现超出实际能力的功能或效果。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.2</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">使用广告法禁用词汇：指商家在商品的主图、标题、属性、商详等关键展示位置，使用被明确禁止的词汇或表述方式进行商品描述。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.3</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">虚假营销活动：指商家在商品宣传、广告或其他营销渠道中使用虚假、误导、夸大或过期的活动信息来吸引消费者参与营销活动，而实际情况与宣传内容不符，影响公平竞争和交易环境的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.4</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">虚假营销服务：指虚构根本不存在的服务或通过虚假、误导性、夸大或隐瞒关键信息的方式推广服务或在商品或服务的宣传中做出不切实际、无法实现或违背客观常识的服务承诺，误导消费者对商品或服务的期望的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.5<span style=\"background-color: #ecf0f1;\">AI</span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ecf0f1;\">假图</span>：禁止利用AI等技术合成方式，呈现显著失真的与实际不符的内容，侵害消费者知情权、误导消费者。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.6</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">其他不符合实际情况的违规宣传：除上述情况外的其他不符合实际情况的违规宣传。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; text-align: left; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.1</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度轻微：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.2</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度一般： 违规商品下架，扣除违约金200元（M2档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.3</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度严重：违规商品下架，扣除违规商品近14天成交金额10%，最低100元，最高10,000元（M3档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.4</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度极其严重：违规商品下架，扣除违规商品近14天成交金额20%，最低300元，最高100,000元（M4档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.5</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></p>\n<h1 id=\"heading-2\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 13pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 16pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; break-after: avoid; font-family: '等线 Light';\"><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台根据违规行为对用户体验造成的伤害程度，从轻到重执行M1到M7档位违约金，具体金额如下：</span></p>\n<table style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-all; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 48.2pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 99.2pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">用户体验伤害分级</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 367.7pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: b