align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">化妆品宣传具备医疗功效；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">普通化妆品宣传具有特殊化妆品功效；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">食品或保健品宣传具有特定的健康效益。</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">保健品商家宣称可以治愈某种疾病，实际没有经过严格的临床试验或获得相关医疗机构的认可；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">药品、医疗器械商家，宣传的功能功效超出商品说明书、备案或注册证的功能功效。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">更多案例可参考<a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: underline; color: #0563c1; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1266955896873947136\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: windowtext;\">发布违规宣传信息案例</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）使用广告法禁用词汇违规情形包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; list-style-type: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">绝对化词汇：如&ldquo;顶级&rdquo;&ldquo;最高级&rdquo;&ldquo;国家级&rdquo;等；</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）虚假营销活动违规情形包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; list-style-type: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在商品信息中使用&ldquo;国家补贴&rdquo;、&ldquo;政府补贴&rdquo;、&ldquo;百亿补贴&rdquo;等字样，明示或暗示商品享有补贴，但实际上未获得相关补贴或政策支持；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在商品信息中使用&ldquo;满xxx元-xx元&rdquo;等字样，宣传满减优惠活动，但实际上没有相应的折扣或优惠；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家参加的活动结束后，未及时调整店铺或商品中的活动信息，使用已结束活动信息；</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）虚假营销服务违规情形包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; list-style-type: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">发布夸大且无法验证的服务承诺，如终身免费维修、无效免费送等相关描述；</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）AI假图违规情形包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; list-style-type: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">利用AI等技术生成虚假商品展示，夸大不实的功能或效果展示等；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">利用AI等技术过度美化导致图片、视频等，导致内容效果失真、内容变形等；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">利用AI等技术生成违背常识、虚构编造、不符合现实或不存在的商品等。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）其他不符合实际情况的违规宣传违规情形包括但不限于以下情形：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; list-style-type: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">过度美化商品不符合客观物理事实，使消费者对商品的真实状态产生错误的认知和期望；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">伪造授权证书、科研成果、排名信息等，诱导或欺骗消费者进行点击或购买的行为。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"heading-3\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 13pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 16pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; break-after: avoid; font-family: '等线 Light';\"><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 23.0667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【附则】</span></span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.1</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家的行为，发生在本规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.2</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东可根据运营情况随时调整本管理规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.3</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有约定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无约定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议；若商家服务协议约定的违约金金额高于规则约定的，京东有权适用协议约定。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.4</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本规则于2026年4月1日修订，于2026年4月8日生效。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
